      "content": "Interesting. I want to dig even deeper into that \"danger\" they feel. Can you write a beat where the conversation turns to the actual physical presence of the black community in town? I want to capture how these men would justify their views on segregation or even more extreme measures to \"maintain order\" if they felt their control was slipping. How would they describe the \"risk\" of letting them mingle or influence the town's social hierarchy?",
